data.description: Check out this amazing property in Moxee, WA! A bright and spacious 4 bed, 2.5 bath home with 2232 sqft. It has updated laminate planks on main floor, a formal living room, a family room, a large master bedroom with a 5 piece bathroom and walk-in closet, an open concept kitchen with a breakfast bar, a laundry room, a 2 car garage, and even RV space outside. Home offers a generous number of windows making the home feel inviting and warm. You've got to see it! Home won't last long. Call today!
